overview: Lena Paul is over the moon when her best friend, Sofi Ryan, sends her a gift from afar. Her heart flutters as she opens the gift, revealing an ornate lamp. When she rubs the lamp with a cloth to give it a shine, a genie, Angela White, suddenly appears! Lena is stunned by the catty and busty beauty as Angela gets down to business, saying that she can grant three wishes.
title: Supernaturally Stacked
